&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Leverage AI &amp;amp; Modern Tools&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;Explore and use AI-powered tools to improve workflows, research customer insights, enhance productivity, and support customer-facing initiatives. Help identify smarter ways of working across the revenue organization.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Turn Data into Insights&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;Analyze customer usage trends, engagement patterns, feedback, and business metrics to uncover opportunities, identify risks, and support data-driven decision making.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Collaborate Across Teams&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;Work closely with Customer Success, Solutions Engineering, Revenue Operations, Sales, Marketing, and Support teams to solve problems, improve processes, and deliver exceptional customer experiences.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Research, Experiment &amp;amp; Innovate&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;Bring fresh ideas and curiosity to the team. Stay up to date with emerging technologies, AI trends, and new ways of working that can help customers and internal teams succeed.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
